targets.query:
from(bucket: "rockoon")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "tracker")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "rockoon")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "tracker")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      
      deg: int(v: r._value),  
      min: int(v: (r._value - float(v: int(v: r._value))) * 60.0),  // Extract minutes
      sec: (((r._value - float(v: int(v: r._value)))) * 60.0 % 1.0) * 60.0
    }))
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "rockoon")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "tracker")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "pressure" or r["_field"] == "temperature" or r["_field"] == "pressure altitude")
  |> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      TimeStamp: r._time,
      pressure: r.pressure,
      temperature: r.temperature,
      altitude: r["pressure altitude"]
    }))

  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
    TimeStamp: r._time,
    Backup_Volt: r["backup power voltage"],
    Primary_Volt: r["primary power voltage"],
    Primary_Current: r["primary power current"],
    Vdd_Volt: r["vdd voltage"],
    Vdd_current: r["vdd current"],
  }))
